column5: welcome moxie, have fun

Been chasing Scales and fins for what seems like forever and even at my age I figure I still have more to learn. Looking forward to Pillaging and stealing all the info I can and maybe share a few tidbits of my own. Thanks to Roy for unlocking the door and letting me in.   Moxie.
Welcome Moxie, you'll enjoy your time on here!  Tony
Welcome to the board. Get ready for the ride of your life
pedro?
